{"tid":2026794,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"鄭松泰跑入立法會 阻止陳凱欣延展限聚令至24/6決議案  限聚令限舖令僅延至10/6","createTime":"2020-05-21T07:38:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-21T09:55:54.000Z","uid":7439,"like":5,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"0c64c6ad58f1c48c2a82cc08a884f78ed144e8c9","tid":2026794,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T07:38:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/9JF8erBQ9P8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F9JF8erBQ9P8&d=JWMo9xAWlgSpyjxIujWPsWaNvfBTe1ydx6p2nKz01sw%3D&h=7d0b355a\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/9JF8erBQ9P8</a><br />\n黃mon前幾分鐘開始睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1713097/org/cfd90414075ee7714207a022401fd1ee.jpg/bNE89UN9a6QjTyPcPMKURTU6wGfTbEfwASzaDQEs2g0?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1713097%2Forg%2Fcfd90414075ee7714207a022401fd1ee.jpg%2FbNE89UN9a6QjTyPcPMKURTU6wGfTbEfwASzaDQEs2g0%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=140266a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<del>陳凱欣議員動議的擬議決議案，議決將2020年4月29日提交立法會會議省覽的《2020年預防及控制疾病條例(修訂附表1及2)公告》、《2020年預防及控制疾病(修訂)(第2號)規例》、《2020年若干到港人士強制檢疫(修訂)(第2號)規例》、《2020年預防及控制疾病(披露資料)(修訂)規例》、《2020年外國地區到港人士強制檢疫(修訂)規例》、《2020年預防及控制疾病(規定及指示)(業務及處所)(修訂)(第2號)規例》和《2020年預防及控制疾病(禁止羣組聚集)(修訂)規例》的<span style=\"color: red;\">修訂期限延展至2020年6月17日的會議，擬議決議案內容載於附錄5。</span><br />\n<br />\n陳凱欣議員動議的另一項擬議決議案，議決將2020年5月6日提交立法會會議省覽的<span style=\"color: red;\">《2020年預防及控制疾病(禁止羣組聚集)(修訂)(第2號)規例》的修訂期限延展至2020年6月24日的會議</span>，擬議決議案內容載於附錄6。</del>"},{"pid":"b549f6597128fea6afe7eab7550409ff5fb0dd49","tid":2026794,"uid":134997,"like":6,"dislike":7,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T07:42:55.000Z","msg":"泛dun仔：熱狗/做show/唔計"},{"pid":"4aeba91d45256ec36afdd9d138ebd6d5d286a1d2","tid":2026794,"uid":13732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T07:44:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91e894b97f91ec7b97c20364a0ddfafeeecf4bf8","tid":2026794,"uid":7439,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T07:45:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.legco.gov.hk/pivote/pivote.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.legco.gov.hk%2Fpivote%2Fpivote.pdf&d=JWMo9xAWlgSpyjxIujWPsWaNvfBTe1ydx6p2nKz01sw%3D&h=fb9fe7dd\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.legco.gov.hk/pivote/pivote.pdf</a><br />\n21/05/2020<br />\n01:19:24  <br />\n動議 MOTION: 延展 3 項根據《預防及控制疾病條例》訂立的附屬法例的修訂期限的擬議決議案<br />\n<br />\n動議人 MOVED BY: 陳凱欣 CHAN Hoi-yan <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.legco.gov.hk/yr19-20/chinese/counmtg/papers/cm20200520-ag-app04-c.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.legco.gov.hk%2Fyr19-20%2Fchinese%2Fcounmtg%2Fpapers%2Fcm20200520-ag-app04-c.pdf&d=JWMo9xAWlgSpyjxIujWPsWaNvfBTe1ydx6p2nKz01sw%3D&h=b2c9dab9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.legco.gov.hk/yr19-20/chinese/counmtg/papers/cm20200520-ag-app04-c.pdf</a><br />\n<blockquote>議決就 2020 年 4 月 22 日提交立法會會議省覽的 <br />\n(a) 《 預防及控制疾病(規定及指示)(業務及處所)規 例》(即刊登於憲報的 2020 年第 31 號法律公告)；<br />\n(b) <span style=\"color: red;\">《預防及控制疾病(禁止羣組聚集)規例》</span>(即刊登於憲報的 2020 年第32 號法律公告)；及<br />\n(c) 《2020 年預防及控制疾病(規定及指示)(業務及處 所)(修 訂)規 例 》(即刊登於憲報的 2020 年第 33 號法律公告)，<br />\n將《釋義及通則條例》(第 1 章)第 34(2)條所提述的附屬法例修訂期限根據該條例第 34(4)條<span style=\"color: red;\">延展至 2020 年 6 月 10 日的會議。</span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>功能 地方 結果<br />\n出席 26 25<br />\n投票 25 25<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">贊成 16 14</span><br />\n反對 9 11<br />\n棄權 0 0<br />\n通過 通過 通過</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n缺席：<br />\n葉劉淑儀 謝偉俊 田北辰 蔣麗芸 <br />\n尹兆堅 朱凱廸 陳淑莊<br />\n<br />\n尹兆堅 朱凱廸 陳淑莊嚟齊係可以14：14否決<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15bb87e64f8d4b572f7353f712270e2ccd9fd503","tid":2026794,"uid":64131,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T07:45:41.000Z","msg":"快唔過莫乃光"},{"pid":"2b1e57ab67c5c9fc1d9058ea8d77542bcc8aaa89","tid":2026794,"uid":7439,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T07:47:29.000Z","msg":"法庭裁定立法會議員陳凱欣並非妥為當選，立法會暫停會議，處理陳凱欣能否繼續參與會議。<br />\n立法會會議正處理延展7項防疫規例修訂期限的擬議決議案，有關決議案由陳凱欣動議。陳凱欣發言期間，<span style=\"color: red;\">莫乃光、鄭松泰</span>提出規程問題，質疑陳凱欣無權動議議案以及發言。<br />\n陳凱欣表示，得悉裁決，指她有上訴期限，而立法會亦面對過有關情況，要求代主席李慧琼裁決。李慧琼一度表示，立法會法律顧問會研究，認為陳凱欣可以發言，<span style=\"color: red;\">其後暫停會議，了解法律顧問意見。</span><br />\n<br />\n李慧琼：OK，又笠了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b4811595083c100e7c885678c9a5949e8844801","tid":2026794,"uid":14238,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T07:47:45.000Z","msg":"預備好問熱狗去咗邊未"},{"pid":"bfa4ea0a3aca3f40dfe4eab0bffb193e6b5ec2ac","tid":2026794,"uid":7439,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T07:48:52.000Z","msg":"陳凱欣反問，如果再出現本地感染或死亡個案，是否由投反對票的議員負責。<br />\n<br />\n咁撚惡<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35d36eaa41364208c607d3db0d68fedc6b09df96","tid":2026794,"uid":77717,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"91e894b97f91ec7b97c20364a0ddfafeeecf4bf8","tid":2026794,"uid":7439,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T07:45:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.legco.gov.hk/pivote/pivote.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.legco.gov.hk%2Fpivote%2Fpivote.pdf&d=JWMo9xAWlgSpyjxIujWPsWaNvfBTe1ydx6p2nKz01sw%3D&h=fb9fe7dd\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.legco.gov.hk/pivote/pivote.pdf</a><br />\n21/05/2020<br />\n01:19:24  <br />\n動議 MOTION: 延展 3 項根據《預防及控制疾病條例》訂立的附屬法例的修訂期限的擬議決議案<br />\n<br />\n動議人 MOVED BY: 陳凱欣 CHAN Hoi-yan <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.legco.gov.hk/yr19-20/chinese/counmtg/papers/cm20200520-ag-app04-c.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.legco.gov.hk%2Fyr19-20%2Fchinese%2Fcounmtg%2Fpapers%2Fcm20200520-ag-app04-c.pdf&d=JWMo9xAWlgSpyjxIujWPsWaNvfBTe1ydx6p2nKz01sw%3D&h=b2c9dab9\" 