sg":"我反問，如果再出現外地傳入感染或死亡個案，是否由反對封關的林鄭負責。"},{"pid":"3f0c3af32e3a9ff20327d53bbc868780995f0a0b","tid":2026794,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T07:51:33.000Z","msg":"大口狗：14日內仲得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0171d04d5fb9d29ec7cf970251d6d55defbd4a6b","tid":2026794,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T07:52:00.000Z","msg":"<em>第542章 《立法會條例》<br />\n17.立法會的程序不受議席空缺影響<br />\n(1)立法會議席空缺並不影響立法會處理事務的權力。<br />\n(2)立法會議席空缺、議員選舉中的欠妥之處或<span style=\"color: red;\">任何人擔任議員的資格有欠妥之處，均不影響立法會程序的有效性。</span><br />\n(3)就本條而言，立法會議席空缺包括立法會在換屆選舉後首次開會時的議席空缺。</em>"},{"pid":"994afe7b9d0e696814ffd7e2bab276d2023e8868","tid":2026794,"uid":136226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T07:53:59.000Z","msg":"睇唔到佢跑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"325b5df0b6719bd88ef12dd478909ea5c34bd2bd","tid":2026794,"uid":41861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b549f6597128fea6afe7eab7550409ff5fb0dd49","tid":2026794,"uid":134997,"like":6,"dislike":7,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T07:42:55.000Z","msg":"泛dun仔：熱狗/做show/唔計"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T07:54:16.000Z","msg":"計啦， 值得一張白票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"642a6fa64db698a75718571e40b99614e4e43ed1","tid":2026794,"uid":199602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"994afe7b9d0e696814ffd7e2bab276d2023e8868","tid":2026794,"uid":136226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T07:53:59.000Z","msg":"睇唔到佢跑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T07:55:16